            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，非p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如，从“2＋2＝4或者3＋3＝6”和“2＋2＝4”不能推出“3＋3≠6”，此推理的第一个前提是相容选言命题，不能由肯定它的一个选言支去否定它的另一个选言支，因为“2＋2＝4”和“3＋3＝6”可以同时成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"subtitle\">（二）不相容选言命题及其推理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">不相容选言命题是断定两种事物情况中有且只有一种情况成立的选言命题。在日常语言中，它有很多表述方式，例如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（1）或为玉碎，或为瓦全。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（2）任一自然数或者是偶数，或者是奇数。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（3）物质形态要么是气体，要么是固体，要么是液体，要么是等离子体，要么是玻色—爱因斯坦冷凝体，要么是费密冷凝体。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（4）要么与我们站在一起去反对恐怖主义，那么你是我们的朋友；要么不与我们站在一起，那么你是我们的敌人。——美国在遭受9·11恐怖袭击后采取了这样的政策。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">我们权且把“要么p，要么q，二者必居其一”当做不相容选言命题的标准形式，其特点是：各个选言支不能同时为真。因此，对于不相容选言命题来说，必有且只有一个选言支为真；若有多个选言支同时为真，或同时为假，则不相容选言命题亦为假。这就是不相容选言命题的逻辑性质。见下表：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"picture\"><$image alt=\"alt\" class=\"calibre3\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/images/images/00017.jpeg\"></$image></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如，“小强所买的那本词典或者是中文词典或者是英文词典”是一个个不相容选言命题，在“小强所买的那本词典是中文词典”和“小强所买的那本词典是英文词典”都假或都真的情况下，它是假的；在其余情况下，它都是真的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">根据不相容选言命题的真值表，不相容选言命题可以用否定词、相容选言联结词“或者”和联言联结词“并且”来定义：“要么p要么q”等值于“‘或者p或者q’并且‘并非p并且q’”。因此，可以不把不相容的“要么，要么”当做初始的或基本的联结词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">根据不相容选言命题的上述性质，不相容选言推理包括下述有效式：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">（Ⅰ）否定肯定式：如果否定一个不相容选言命题的一个选言支，则必须肯定它的另一个选言支。其形式是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
