        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如：“或为玉碎，或为瓦全。宁为玉碎，所以，不为瓦全。”再如：“要么继续闭关锁国而落后挨打，要么实行改革开放而走向富强；我们必须实行改革开放而走向富强，所以，我们不能再继续闭关锁国而落后挨打。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">讲一个用选言推理解智力思考题的例子：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">一个街道上有三户人家，各有祖孙三代在同一个工厂里做工，分别做车工、钳工、勤杂工。一户的祖孙三代之间工种各不相同，三户的同辈人之间工种各不相同。已知爷爷做车工的那家，其孙子不做勤杂工，请问这三家的祖孙三代各干什么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">根据题中给定的条件，我们实际上有这样的不相容选言命题：x要么做车工，要么做钳工，要么做勤杂工；再由于一户的祖孙三代之间工种各不相同，爷爷做车工的那家，既然孙子不做勤杂工，也不能做车工，所以必做钳工，父亲不能做车工，也不能做钳工，只能做勤杂工；第二家的爷爷只能做钳工或者勤杂工，假设他做钳工，则父亲只能做车工或勤杂工，由于第一家的父亲做勤杂工，所以他必做车工，而孙子只能做勤杂工；于是，第三家的爷爷做勤杂工，父亲做钳工，孙子做车工。解这道题，所用的全部是选言推理。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">关于选言命题，应该注意以下两点：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">第一，一个选言命题究竟是相容的还是不相容的，没有专用的形式识别标记，只能看其中的各个选言支是否能够同时为真：能够同时为真的，是相容选言命题；不能同时为真的，是不相容选言命题。这是因为：联结词“或者，或者”既可在相容意义上使用，也可在不相容意义上使用。“要么，要么”同样既可在相容意义上使用，也可在不相容意义上使用。因此，区分相容选言命题和不相容选言命题，不能只看联结词，而应重点看它们的真值情况。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">第二，如果一个选言命题穷尽了所有的选言支，则该选言命题必真；假若选言支不穷尽，则选言命题有可能为假。例如，刑侦人员根据某一犯罪现场的证据，作出推测：“罪犯或者是甲或者是乙”。但后来的侦查证实这一推测是假的，真正的罪犯是丙，他伪造了现场证据。这里，刑侦人员开始的推测就过于武断，没有考虑到其他可能情况。不过，当遇到复杂情形时，穷尽所有的选言支既无必要也不可能，只能是依靠证据作出最有可能成立的推测。并且，一个真的选言命题不一定穷尽了所有的选言支，例如，根据小张的长相和口音，可以作出正确的推测：“小张或者是广东人，或者是广西人。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"title1\">四　假言命题和假言推理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">假言命题是断定事物情况之间的条件关系的复合命题。条件关系分为三种：充分条件、必要条件和充分必要条件。相应地，假言命题也分为三种：充分条件假言命题，必要条件假言命题，充分必要条件假言命题。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"subtitle\">（一）充分条件假言命题及其推理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">如果有p就有q，则p是q的充分条件。充分条件假言命题是断定p是q充分条件的假言命题，它在自然语言中有多种表述方式。例如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（1）只要勤奋耕耘，总会有所收获。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（2）如果身体过胖，就容易患上各种疾病。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（3）假如没有地心引力的话，树上的苹果就不会落地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（4）如果所有的金子都是闪光的，则有些闪光的东西是金子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（5）要是你能解决哥德巴赫猜想，我就能拔着自己的头发上天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（6）如果你是个傻瓜，那么一言不发是最聪明的；如果你是个聪明人，那么一言不发是最愚蠢的。——一位哲学家在回答“在交际场合一言不发好不好”的问题时如是说。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">有时候，表达充分条件关系的联结词还可以省略。例如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（7）锲而不舍，金石可镂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（8）人心齐，泰山移。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（9）招手即停。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">我们把“如果p则q”当做充分条件假言命题的标准表达形式，其中p为前件，q为后件。只有在p真q假的情况下，“如果p则q”才是假的，在其他情况下都是真的。见下表：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"picture\"><$image alt=\"alt\" class=\"calibre3\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/images/images/00018.jpeg\"></$image></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">例如，充分条件假言命题“如果天下雨，那么会议延期”，只有在天下雨但会议未延期的情况下才是假的，在其他情况下都是真的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">根据这个真值表，一个充分条件假言命题，只要其前件是假的，或者其后件是真的，它本身就是真的，即：“如果p则q”等值于“或者非p或者q”。并且，如果p真并且q假，则“如果p那么q”就是假的，并且只有在这种情况下，“如果p那么q”才是假的，即：“如果p则q”等值于“并非（p并且非q）”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">请看下面的例证：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">红星中学的四位老师在高考前对某理科毕业班学生的前景进行推测，他们特别关注班里的两个尖子生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">张老师说：“如果余涌能考上清华，那么方宁也能考上清华。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">李老师说：“依我看这个班没人能考上清华。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">王老师说：“不管方宁能否考上清华，余涌考不上清华。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">赵老师说：“我看方宁考不上清华，但余涌能考上清华。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">高考的结果证明，四位老师中只有一人的推测成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">如果上述断定是真的，则以下哪项也一定是真的？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">A．李老师的推测成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">B．王老师的推测成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">C．赵老师的推测不成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">D．如果方宁考不上清华大学，则张老师的推测成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">E．如果方宁考上了清华大学，则张老师的推测成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">解析：答案是E。题干中张老师和赵老师的判断形式分别为“如果p则q”和“p并且非q”，由前面的讨论可知，它们是互相矛盾的，根据矛盾律和排中律，其中必有一个推测成立且只有一个成立。又由给定条件，四人中只有一人的推测成立，因此李老师和王老师的推测均不成立，即有人考上了大学，且这个人就是余涌。因此，如果方宁也考上了清华，则只有张老师的推测成立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">根据充分条件假言命题的上述性质，充分条件假言推理的有效式包括：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">（1）肯定前件式：如果肯定一个充分条件假言命题，并且肯定它的前件，那么，必须肯定它的后件。其形式是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">如果p，那么q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如：“如果官员甲拥有不受监控的权力，官员甲就很容易导致腐败；官员甲确实拥有不受监控的权力，所以，官员甲很容易腐败。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">再讲一个故事：有一次美术学院的入学考试是命题作画：“深山藏古寺”。最后交上来的一幅幅画面上，只见山峰叠着山峰，山丛连着山丛，但又在画面的不同角落露出寺庙的尖顶、房瓦等等。唯有一副画面上，根本见不到寺庙的踪影，但顺着画面从上往下看，只见山脚下有两个和尚正在往山上抬水。看到最后这一幅画，我们马上能够想到：山上必有寺庙。这是因为，我们头脑中进行了这样一个推理：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">如果有和尚往山上抬水，山上必有寺庙；这幅画上有和尚往山上抬水。所以，这幅画上看不见的某处必有寺庙，只不过被山石和树木“藏”起来了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">显然，后一幅画的作者比其他作者更高明，因为他的画给读者留下了想象的空间、发展的余地，并且还能唤醒读者的审美经验和文化感受，例如中国人一看到这幅画，马上会想到这样的谚语：一个和尚挑水吃，两个和尚抬水吃，三个和尚没水吃，从而发出会心的一笑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">（2）否定后件式：如果肯定一个充分条件假言命题，并且否定它的后件，则必须否定它的前件。其形式是：</p></div>"
        },
