            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，非q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">和肯定后件式：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">如果p，那么q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">是无效的。例如：“如果长期躺在床上看书，就会患近视眼；我从不躺在床上看书，所以，我不会患近视眼。”显然，这个推理是无效的，因为近视眼还可能由遗传产生。再如：“如果王浩是美国总统，他肯定也是人；王浩确实是人，所以，他肯定是美国总统。”这个推理的无效性也是显然的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"subtitle\">（二）必要条件假言命题及其推理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">如果p是q的不可缺少的条件，即无p就无q，则p是q的必要条件。必要条件假言命题是断定p是q的必要条件的假言命题。在自然语言中，其表述方式是多种多样的。例如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（1）除非通过考试，否则不予录取。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（2）仅当明天天晴，我们才去郊游。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（3）不积跬步无以致千里，不积细流无以成江海。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（4）做学问是一门笨功夫，只有坚持不懈，才能有所成就。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（5）若要人不知，除非己莫为。（这相当于说：只有己莫为，才会人不知。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">在逻辑学中，必要条件假言命题的标准形式是“只有p，才q”，其中p为前件，q为后件。只有在前件假后件真的情况下，一个必要条件假言命题才是假的，在前件真后件真、前件真后件假、前件假后件假的情况下，它都是真的。这就是必要条件假言命题的逻辑性质。见下表：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"picture\"><$image alt=\"alt\" class=\"calibre3\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/images/images/00019.jpeg\"></$image></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">例如，必要条件假言命题“除非考试及格，否则不予录取”，只有在“考试不及格却予以录取”的情况下才是假的，在其他情况下（例如“考试及格却未予录取”）都是真的。再如，如果有人坚持说“只有乡下人才长寿”，但经调查发现，城市里有不少人是百岁寿星，这一事实就证明那个人所说的话是假的；但如果发现有的乡下人不长寿，却不能证明该句话为假。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">根据真值表可以看出，如果p是q的充分条件，则q是p的必要条件；如果p是q的必要条件，则q是p的充分条件。也就是说，“如果p，那么q”等值于“只有q，才p”；“只有p，才q”等值于“如果q，那么p”；“只有p，才q”等值于“如果非p，那么非q”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">这说明，必要条件假言命题可以用充分条件假言命题来刻画和定义，因此，可以不把“只有……才……”当做初始的或基本的联结词，而当做一个被定义的联结词。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">根据必要条件假言命题的上述性质，必要条件假言推理的有效式包括：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">（1）否定前件式：如果肯定一个必要条件假言命题，并且否定其前件，则要否定其后件。其形式是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">只有p，才q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">非p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，非q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如：“只有陈梦溪年满18岁，他才有选举权和被选举权；陈梦溪年仅16岁，所以他没有选举权和被选举权。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">（2）肯定后件式：如果肯定一个必要条件假言命题，并且肯定其后件，则要肯定其前件。其形式是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">只有p，才q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如，一个小女儿问妈妈：“妈妈，您头上为什么长出了白头发呀？”妈妈回答说：“因为女儿不听话，妈妈才长出白头发。”小女儿眨巴眨巴眼睛，想了一想，说：“我现在才知道，外婆的头发为什么全都白了。”显然，小女儿正在进行必要条件假言命题的肯定后件式推理：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">只有女儿不听话，妈妈才长出白头发。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">外婆的头发全都白了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，外婆的女儿——妈妈不听话。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">这个推理是有效的，妈妈不正确的教育方式被聪明的女儿钻了空子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">必要条件假言推理的无效式有肯定前件式：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">只有p，才q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">和否定后件式：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">只有p，才q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">非q</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">————</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以，非p</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext4\">例如：“只有夏闯不循规蹈矩，他才能大有作为；夏闯不循规蹈矩，所以，夏闯一定大有作为。”这是必要条件假言推理的肯定前件式，明显是无效的。再如：“只有老王不畏劳苦，他才能有所成就；老王一生谈不上有什么成就，因此，老王必定是怕苦怕累之人。”这个推理的前提可能都真，而结论却可能假，因而是无效的。事实上，老王不但不怕苦怕累，反而非常能吃苦，数十年如一日，头悬梁，锥刺股，寒窗秉烛夜读书，却没有弄出什么成就来。我们不能因此轻视和鄙视老王，相反，鲁迅对此类人等给予了极大的赞扬：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">所以中国一向就少有失败的英雄，少有韧性的反抗，少有单身鏖战的武人，少有敢抚哭叛徒的吊客。见胜兆则纷纷聚集，见败兆则纷纷逃亡。战具比我们精利的欧美人，战具未必比我们精利的匈奴蒙古满州人，都如入无人之境，“土崩瓦解”这四个字，真是形容得有自知之明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">多有“不耻最后”的人的民族，无论什么事，怕总不会一下子就“土崩瓦解”的。我每看运动会时，常常这样想：优胜者固然可敬，但那虽然落后而仍非跑至终点不止的竞技者，和见了这样的竞技者而肃然不笑的看客，乃正是中国将来的脊梁。<sup class=\"suptext1\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001641\">〔3〕</$link></sup></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"subtitle\">（三）充分必要条件假言推理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">如果有p就有q，无p就无q，则p是q的充分必要条件。充分必要条件假言命题就是断定p是q的充分必要条件的假言命题，由“当且仅当”这类联结词连接两个支命题而形成。例如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（1）一个三角形的三边相等，当且仅当，它的三内角都是60°。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（2）X⊆Y，当且仅当，（∀x）（x∈A→x∈B）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（3）张猛是单身汉，当且仅当，他是未婚男子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">“当且仅当”这一联结词通常只在数学、逻辑及其他精确科学中出现，在社会科学和人们的日常交谈中很少使用。在日常语言中，人们要表述一个充分必要条件假言命题时，常常分成两句话，前一句话说前件是后件的充分条件，后一句话说前件是后件的必要条件。例如：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（1）人不犯我，我不犯人；人若犯我，我必犯人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext3\">（2）如果公民年满18岁，则他有选举权和被选举权；只有公民年满18岁，他才有选举权和被选举权。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\"><br class=\"calibre2\"></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">显然，当前件和后件同真或同假时，一个充分必要条件假言命题为真，在其他情况下都是假的。见下表：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"picture\"><$image alt=\"alt\" class=\"calibre3\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/images/images/00020.jpeg\"></$image></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/767506b8c19e4254/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-767506b8c19e4254-43189b twpub-767506b8c19e4254-9882b5\"><p class=\"normaltext1\">充分必要条件假言推理的四个有效式列举如下：</p></div>"
        },
